data.title: Libra Bronze Blocks Family of Three Sculpture
data.meta_description:
Inspired by our best selling friendship bench, this beautiful resin sculpture celebrates timeless familial love. As art often draws from love, this sculpture of a family shows the subtle beauty of the love between a household. 

Cast in top quality resin and finished in detailed bronze, this is an ornate and detailed piece that celebrates true love. Fantstic as a gift for loved ones or to celebrate your own love with a partner this decorative piece is guaranteed to warm hearts. Dimensions: 17.8x6.4x22.8 (WxDxH cm)
